com.ausregistry.jtoolkit2.se

Class ReceiveSE

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ausregistry.jtoolkit2.se.ReceiveSE
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ArExtensionResponse, Greeting, Response

    public abstract class ReceiveSE
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Handles basic processing of all EPP packets received by the client. Parsing of the received XML document is the only responsibility of this class. Uses the maintenance, debug, support and user level loggers.
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
